1
00:00:13,010 --> 00:00:15,810
[Episode 30]

2
00:02:40,383 --> 00:02:40,766
Xiaoman.

3
00:02:44,047 --> 00:02:44,846
Xiaoman.

4
00:02:45,047 --> 00:02:45,646
What's wrong?

5
00:02:45,647 --> 00:02:47,046
I've been poisoned.

6
00:02:55,647 --> 00:02:56,886
My dear Yimo,

7
00:02:57,207 --> 00:02:58,166
I've taken poison.

8
00:02:58,767 --> 00:03:00,326
The antidote is with the He family's steward.

9
00:03:00,487 --> 00:03:02,326
Use it to bargain with Yu Shi'an for your safety.

10
00:03:08,967 --> 00:03:09,766
Who did this?

11
00:03:10,207 --> 00:03:12,206
Zhou Yimo...

12
00:03:12,767 --> 00:03:13,446
Xiaoman.

13
00:03:16,967 --> 00:03:17,806
Zhou Yimo!

14
00:03:17,967 --> 00:03:18,686
Guards!

15
00:03:21,807 --> 00:03:22,926
Guards!

16
00:03:26,367 --> 00:03:26,886
Marshal.

17
00:03:27,327 --> 00:03:28,326
This poison is rare.

18
00:03:29,007 --> 00:03:30,206
The antibiotics to counteract it

19
00:03:30,207 --> 00:03:31,406
can only be obtained from Peking Hospital.

20
00:03:32,047 --> 00:03:33,446
And the toxin is spreading rapidly.

21
00:03:33,687 --> 00:03:35,006
By the time we get it from Peking Hospital,

22
00:03:35,527 --> 00:03:36,686
even if Madam survives,

23
00:03:37,527 --> 00:03:38,846
relying solely on our medication,

24
00:03:39,247 --> 00:03:39,966
she might...

25
00:03:40,367 --> 00:03:41,366
suffer brain damage.

26
00:04:06,647 --> 00:04:07,126
Marshal.

27
00:04:07,567 --> 00:04:08,166
Marshal.

28
00:04:08,207 --> 00:04:09,086
Marshal.

29
00:04:24,247 --> 00:04:24,846
Marshal,

30
00:04:25,207 --> 00:04:26,086
he's been brought to you.

31
00:04:27,247 --> 00:04:28,086
Yu Shi'an.

32
00:04:28,807 --> 00:04:29,926
The antidote will be here soon.

33
00:04:48,927 --> 00:04:49,646
Yu Shi'an.

34
00:04:51,047 --> 00:04:52,846
This is a simple and clean deal.

35
00:04:53,527 --> 00:04:55,366
Your beloved Ye Xiaoman's life

36
00:04:56,527 --> 00:04:57,966
in exchange for my freedom.

37
00:05:02,847 --> 00:05:03,326
Marshal.

38
00:05:03,887 --> 00:05:04,526
The antidote.

39
00:05:07,327 --> 00:05:08,246
Hurry.

40
00:05:09,487 --> 00:05:11,006
Ye Zhiqiu can't wait.

41
00:05:12,287 --> 00:05:13,606
If anything happens to Xiaoman,

42
00:05:13,607 --> 00:05:14,806
I'll kill your entire family.

43
00:06:00,367 --> 00:06:00,726
Marshal.

44
00:06:01,287 --> 00:06:02,046
She's out of danger.

45
00:06:05,607 --> 00:06:06,606
When will she wake up?

46
00:06:07,167 --> 00:06:07,886
After the IV drip,

47
00:06:07,927 --> 00:06:08,846
she should wake soon.

48
00:06:09,487 --> 00:06:10,326
Thanks to your antidote,

49
00:06:10,607 --> 00:06:11,966
she nearly didn't make it.

50
00:06:51,247 --> 00:06:51,806
Marshal.

51
00:06:53,047 --> 00:06:53,846
Trouble.

52
00:07:03,727 --> 00:07:04,606
Yu Shi'an.

53
00:07:05,287 --> 00:07:07,086
I've come from Peking,

54
00:07:07,167 --> 00:07:08,926
I'm the newly appointed Police Chief,

55
00:07:09,287 --> 00:07:10,326
Liang Shuping.

56
00:07:11,087 --> 00:07:13,086
You conspired with former Marshal Lu Huaigu

57
00:07:13,647 --> 00:07:15,726
to bribe police officials

58
00:07:16,847 --> 00:07:17,806
for opium trafficking.

59
00:07:18,487 --> 00:07:19,846
It's irrefutable proof.

60
00:07:19,967 --> 00:07:20,926
This is the arrest warrant.

61
00:07:27,607 --> 00:07:28,606
Zhou Yimo.

62
00:07:28,967 --> 00:07:30,486
You must have planned this

63
00:07:30,807 --> 00:07:32,286
before your arrest.

64
00:07:34,607 --> 00:07:35,526
Yu Shi'an.

65
00:07:48,047 --> 00:07:48,606
Xiaoman.

66
00:07:50,287 --> 00:07:51,086
You're better.

67
00:07:53,687 --> 00:07:54,686
That's wonderful.

68
00:07:57,047 --> 00:07:58,046
I was poisoned,

69
00:08:00,047 --> 00:08:01,286
just not seriously.

70
00:08:03,687 --> 00:08:04,886
Everything at the hospital

71
00:08:06,687 --> 00:08:07,846
was an act for you.

72
00:08:09,287 --> 00:08:11,166
All to make you release Zhou Yimo.

73
00:08:22,447 --> 00:08:23,046
Xiaoman.

74
00:08:24,807 --> 00:08:25,486
How could you...

75
00:08:59,047 --> 00:08:59,926
Zhou Yimo!

76
00:09:07,607 --> 00:09:08,526
In this lifetime,

77
00:09:10,887 --> 00:09:12,206
I've never fought for anything

78
00:09:16,407 --> 00:09:17,926
but I've lost only to you.

79
00:09:20,487 --> 00:09:21,206
Yu Shi'an.

80
00:09:22,287 --> 00:09:23,166
Yu Shi'an.

81
00:09:24,287 --> 00:09:25,006
Xiaoman.

82
00:09:29,327 --> 00:09:30,646
Remember that game

83
00:09:30,927 --> 00:09:32,086
we played as kids?

84
00:09:34,927 --> 00:09:36,766
I just wanted to tease you a bit

85
00:09:37,687 --> 00:09:38,566
like when we were kids.

86
00:09:41,567 --> 00:09:42,126
Yu Shi'an.

87
00:09:42,487 --> 00:09:43,086
Don't!

88
00:10:08,087 --> 00:10:09,086
Xiaoman, don't cry.

89
00:10:09,327 --> 00:10:25,686
I'll show you something cool.

90
00:10:25,687 --> 00:10:26,326
Shi'an!

91
00:10:26,327 --> 00:10:27,166
Are you okay?

92
00:10:27,167 --> 00:10:28,686
You're not really dead, are you?

93
00:10:29,007 --> 00:10:30,286
You can't die!

94
00:10:30,287 --> 00:10:32,686
Who'll protect me if you die?

95
00:10:36,407 --> 00:10:38,526
Don't be afraid.

96
00:10:39,567 --> 00:10:40,686
When I grow up,

97
00:10:40,687 --> 00:10:42,486
I'll replace this with a real gun

98
00:10:42,847 --> 00:10:43,886
and protect you for life.

99
00:10:44,447 --> 00:10:45,166
Okay?

100
00:10:47,887 --> 00:10:48,926
Shi'an!

101
00:11:19,527 --> 00:11:20,166
Look.

102
00:11:20,287 --> 00:11:21,046
Zhou Mansion.

103
00:11:21,047 --> 00:11:22,166
Zhou Mansion is sealed off.

104
00:11:22,287 --> 00:11:23,726
This is too ominous. Let's go!

105
00:11:24,327 --> 00:11:26,286
The former Master Zhou died of illness.

106
00:11:26,647 --> 00:11:27,966
The second young master was shot.

107
00:11:28,407 --> 00:11:30,286
The madam and second concubine were burned to death.

108
00:11:30,287 --> 00:11:31,726
The Third concubine was strangled.

109
00:11:32,327 --> 00:11:33,446
The steward died too.

110
00:11:33,647 --> 00:11:34,846
The driver died.

111
00:11:34,887 --> 00:11:36,126
The maids died.

112
00:11:36,927 --> 00:11:38,806
Another maid drowned in the pond.

113
00:11:38,807 --> 00:11:40,966
Now they've all turned into ghosts.

114
00:11:41,647 --> 00:11:43,766
The Zhou family was so glorious before.

115
00:11:44,327 --> 00:11:45,566
Indeed it was.

116
00:12:09,487 --> 00:12:10,446
Sister.

117
00:12:27,287 --> 00:12:27,806
Sister.

118
00:12:36,287 --> 00:12:37,406
Damn girl!

119
00:12:37,767 --> 00:12:38,886
Where has she disappeared to again?

120
00:12:39,687 --> 00:12:40,966
She must have gone to madam's place

121
00:12:40,967 --> 00:12:41,886
to slack off again.

122
00:12:43,847 --> 00:12:45,566
I'll give her a good beating later.

123
00:12:46,327 --> 00:12:47,366
Who

124
00:12:47,447 --> 00:12:49,046
made my Second concubine angry?

125
00:12:50,287 --> 00:12:51,326
Master.

126
00:12:53,007 --> 00:12:54,166
In this household,

127
00:12:54,487 --> 00:12:55,966
madam manages everything.

128
00:12:56,527 --> 00:12:58,966
The servants and maids all brush me off.

129
00:13:00,767 --> 00:13:01,926
If any servant

130
00:13:02,287 --> 00:13:04,126
servant or maid dares to brush you off,

131
00:13:04,647 --> 00:13:07,166
I'll sell them all off.

132
00:13:08,407 --> 00:13:09,926
Master, you truly care for me.

133
00:13:34,807 --> 00:13:35,206
Father.

134
00:13:40,167 --> 00:13:40,806
Chen.

135
00:13:41,447 --> 00:13:42,926
You've performed well recently.

136
00:13:43,407 --> 00:13:44,886
You've managed affairs inside and outside

137
00:13:45,687 --> 00:13:47,166
the mansion in perfect order.

138
00:13:48,527 --> 00:13:49,406
Thank you for your praise, Father.

139
00:13:49,807 --> 00:13:51,006
I think you're too kind.

140
00:13:52,047 --> 00:13:52,326
By the way,

141
00:13:52,807 --> 00:13:54,686
it will be your birthday soon.

142
00:13:55,287 --> 00:13:56,286
I have prepared

143
00:13:56,567 --> 00:13:58,006
a small gift for you.

144
00:14:04,447 --> 00:14:06,046
It does bear

145
00:14:06,687 --> 00:14:07,806
some resemblance to me.

146
00:14:10,127 --> 00:14:11,206
Your craftsmanship

147
00:14:11,527 --> 00:14:12,886
has improved, significantly.

148
00:14:14,167 --> 00:14:15,406
Thank you for your praise, Father.

149
00:14:16,287 --> 00:14:16,886
Master.

150
00:14:17,127 --> 00:14:17,766
Second Young Master,

151
00:14:17,807 --> 00:14:18,766
at the wood carving shop,

152
00:14:18,807 --> 00:14:19,526
there's a matter

153
00:14:19,527 --> 00:14:20,886
that requires your attention.

154
00:14:21,887 --> 00:14:22,926
I will go attend to it first.

155
00:14:24,767 --> 00:14:26,406
Remember to come back for dinner.

156
00:14:27,807 --> 00:14:28,526
Go ahead.

157
00:14:28,527 --> 00:14:29,446
Let's go, Second Young Master.

158
00:14:31,647 --> 00:14:32,806
Today is the fifteenth.

159
00:14:32,807 --> 00:14:34,686
Later, go to Wanxiang Temple to make offerings.

160
00:14:35,047 --> 00:14:35,406
Yes.

161
00:14:35,807 --> 00:14:36,806
You're kind-hearted.

162
00:14:37,007 --> 00:14:38,046
Every first and fifteenth,

163
00:14:38,047 --> 00:14:39,286
you make offerings to the Bodhisattva.

164
00:14:39,567 --> 00:14:40,806
This has accumulated much good karma

165
00:14:40,807 --> 00:14:41,926
for our Second Young Master.

166
00:14:42,807 --> 00:14:43,846
I only hope that Chen

167
00:14:43,847 --> 00:14:44,926
can be happy

168
00:14:45,047 --> 00:14:46,166
and do what he wants to do.

169
00:14:53,487 --> 00:14:54,046
Here.

170
00:14:55,967 --> 00:14:56,846
What is this?

171
00:14:56,967 --> 00:14:58,286
It's pastries I made.

172
00:15:01,167 --> 00:15:01,886
Try some.

173
00:15:03,527 --> 00:15:04,286
You try first.

174
00:15:27,407 --> 00:15:27,926
Sister!

175
00:15:31,687 --> 00:15:32,926
I finally found you!

176
00:15:37,327 --> 00:15:38,166
Silly sister.

177
00:15:38,807 --> 00:15:39,926
Everyone else has left.

178
00:15:40,287 --> 00:15:41,446
Why haven't you left yet?

179
00:15:42,407 --> 00:15:43,686
I was waiting for you.

180
00:15:45,687 --> 00:15:46,566
This manor

181
00:15:46,647 --> 00:15:47,726
is too large.

182
00:15:48,007 --> 00:15:48,926
Once people enter,

183
00:15:48,967 --> 00:15:50,526
they can never leave.

184
00:15:51,687 --> 00:15:52,326
But

185
00:15:52,927 --> 00:15:54,406
I know how to get out.

186
00:15:55,727 --> 00:15:56,246
Come.

187
00:15:56,767 --> 00:15:57,526
I'll take you away.

188
00:16:04,207 --> 00:16:04,806
Here.

189
00:16:14,407 --> 00:16:15,446
Go to class now.

190
00:16:15,527 --> 00:16:17,126
I need to go back to work.

191
00:16:21,487 --> 00:16:22,606
Don't miss me too much.

192
00:16:27,247 --> 00:16:28,526
When the New Year comes,

193
00:16:29,287 --> 00:16:30,286
I will come to your school

194
00:16:30,287 --> 00:16:31,126
to bring you home.

195
00:16:33,687 --> 00:16:34,406
New Year...

196
00:16:36,887 --> 00:16:38,326
I'll wait for you to bring me home.

197
00:18:11,167 --> 00:18:11,566
Let's go.

198
00:18:12,167 --> 00:18:12,806
I'll get you home.
